<img id="big_unit" class="big_u69" src="gpack/travian_default/img/x.gif" alt="Nomarch" title="Nomarch" /><div id="t_desc">The Nomarch is the Egyptian provincial governor and diplomat. His authority and eloquent speeches can sway the loyalty of enemy villages. He is the administrative counterpart to the Hun Logades, able to bring enemy settlements under Egyptian rule through persuasion and political maneuvering.</div>
